              alt="Intersect Power"></div>
            <span class="party-name">Intersect Power</span>
          </div>
          <p class="party-sub">2.2 GW solar + 2.4 GWh BESS; $15B AUM in ops or construction; co-located data center energy parks (TX &amp; CA)</p>
        </div>
      </td>
      <td>
        <div class="party-cell">
          <span class="p-label">Buyer</span>
          <div class="party-row">
            <div class="logo-box"><img
              src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/2f/Google_2015_logo.svg/200px-Google_2015_logo.svg.png"
              onerror="this.closest('.logo-box').outerHTML='<div class=\'logo-init\' style=\'background:#4285F4\'>G</div>'"
              alt="Google"></div>
            <span class="party-name buyer">Google / Alphabet</span>
          </div>
          <p class="party-sub">Existing minority holder (prior $800M investment in Intersect)</p>
        </div>
      </td>
      <td class="val">~$4.75B<br><small style="font-family:inherit;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)">cash + debt assumption</small></td>
