          <a class="src" href="https://www.pv-tech.org/google-finalises-intersect-acquisition-to-bring-data-centre-power-in-house/" target="_blank">PV-Tech</a>
          <a class="src" href="https://www.solarpowerworldonline.com/2026/03/after-google-takeover-intersect-changes-name-to-ipx-power/" target="_blank">Solar Power World</a>
          <a class="src" href="https://abc.xyz/investor/news/news-details/2025/Alphabet-Announces-Agreement-to-Acquire-Intersect-to-Advance-U-S--Energy-Innovation-2025-DVIuVDM9wW/default.aspx" target="_blank">Alphabet IR</a>
          <a class="src" href="https://pv-magazine-usa.com/2026/01/02/google-acquires-clean-energy-developer-intersect-power-for-nearly-5-billion/" target="_blank">PV Magazine USA</a>
